689
00:31:02,461 --> 00:31:03,694
To jest, sve do Roseina muža

690
00:31:03,796 --> 00:31:05,295
Prekinuo dovod vode

691
00:31:05,397 --> 00:31:07,364
I prodali su cijelo svoje imanje Rose Pruett.

692
00:31:07,466 --> 00:31:08,899
Pruetti su uzeli o'neillovu zemlju.

693
00:31:09,001 --> 00:31:11,268
Kupili su ga tehnički, ali za sitne pare.

694
00:31:12,504 --> 00:31:13,503
