00:38:20,365 --> 00:38:21,498
Je li ovo tvoj pasivno-agresivni,

832
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:23,199
Emocionalno zakržljao način kazivanja

833
00:38:23,302 --> 00:38:25,302
Stvarno ti je stalo do mene malog starog?

834
00:38:27,372 --> 00:38:28,672
Vidimo se, max.

835
00:38:32,778 --> 00:38:33,810
Vidimo se, earl.

